{"tid":2446964,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中共既「香港人問題的最終解決方案」","createTime":"2021-03-15T00:36:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T05:22:30.000Z","uid":247211,"like":17,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"efab4ac6bd9e8e2e1beb03d995dc8a8afc55d036","tid":2446964,"uid":247211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T00:36:07.000Z","msg":"1942年1月舉行的萬湖會議確定大規模屠殺猶太人的方針，決定自西向東徹底清洗歐洲猶太人，將其全部送往東方佔領區，通過繁重勞役加以消滅，倖存者則處死，使猶太民族徹底滅絕。 在具體實施中，波蘭、匈牙利、希臘和南斯拉夫等國的猶太人大部在毒氣室遇害；奧地利、捷克斯洛伐克、荷蘭和比利時的猶太人半數遭殺；丹麥和保加利亞的猶太人在當地民眾的保護下大部倖存。根據納粹德國殘存文件統計，歐洲地區約有510萬猶太人成為該計劃的犧牲品，但實際數字估計可達600萬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歐洲地區約有510萬猶太人成為該計劃的犧牲品，但實際數字估計可達<span class=\"red\">600萬</span><br />\n香港人口750萬 - 新港人約150萬 = <span class=\"red\">600萬</span><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">MATCH</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.timesofisrael.com/www/uploads/2013/10/Selection_Birkenau_ramp-e1398598639275-1024x640.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.timesofisrael.com%2Fwww%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F10%2FSelection_Birkenau_ramp-e1398598639275-1024x640.jpg&h=771328ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n到時一車車港豬咁送入集中營<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e67f9d448d599e98b415794caf9bce79c1107f60","tid":2446964,"uid":54975,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T01:13:56.000Z","msg":"香港人問題的最終解決方案<br />\n<br />\n就係<br />\n<br />\n解決香港人問題的最終方案 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c706a39e22a7a922226fa267752e138fd386edb1","tid":2446964,"uid":247211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T01:31:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hk